Package: SCtools
Title: Tools for Synthetic Controls Analysis
Version: 0.2
Date: 2018-05-22
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Bruno",
           family = "Castanho Silva",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bcsilva@wiso.uni-koeln.de")
           )
Maintainer: Bruno Castanho Silva <bcsilva@wiso.uni-koeln.de>
Description: A set of functions to extend the synthetic controls analyses 
    performed by the package Synth. Includes generating and plotting placebos, 
    significance tests and plots, and calculating average treatment effects 
    for multiple treated units.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
    covr
Imports: 
    Hmisc,
    Synth,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
